<p>Trackers also allow for&nbsp;<strong>efficient asset allocation</strong>&nbsp;by spreading investments across different cryptocurrencies, thus mitigating risk while maximizing potential gains. Crucially, these tracking platforms offer an easy way to&nbsp;<strong>regularly optimize your portfolio</strong>&nbsp;&#8211; a key strategy in achieving your financial goals as per important facts.</p>



